{"tid":763714,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇熟裝修既巴打幫手， 屋企爆咸水喉，全屋浸晒","createTime":"2018-08-01T10:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T10:51:34.000Z","uid":37326,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"741ef4188c4c81762e0ae4c91927bcf33872f328","tid":763714,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:50:39.000Z","msg":"件事係咁既：<br />\n個單位係居屋黎，2016年買入，全屋裝修過晒<br />\n話說前日我老婆係廁所痾痾下尿，突然之間&quot;boom&quot;一聲， 條咸水喉開關制個位爆左，超高水壓既咸水瘋狂爆出，我即刻衝落去管理處叫人關水制， 結果搞左15分鐘先關到<br />\n<br />\n由於d 水太大， 15分鐘d 水已經浸晒出廳，過晒腳眼位置， 後來我叫左人上黎抽走晒d 水， 尋日再搵人整返條咸水喉。<br />\n<br />\n咁我有買家居保險，尋日打左俾保險果邊，佢今朝派左公證行既人上黎視察屋企既情況，條友同我講總之全屋有因為呢次意外而損壞既家俬電器都可以同保險公司claim , 但就要叫人黎報價或上網搵返一件差唔多樣既家俬做參考價格。<br />\n<br />\n但我而家係最擔心個地板， 我屋企地板雖然唔係木地板， 係瓷磚， 但我聽人講d 咸水會一樣流落去瓷磚底d 沙度， 一段時間之間就會發霉同會有d 蚊螆發出黎，我問過公證行，佢話最好等一兩個月到果d 地磚真係發生問題再同佢講。<br />\n<br />\n我就諗既然都咁嚴重，不如全屋裝修過晒，同盡快搞，有冇熟裝修既巴打知道d 地磚咁樣浸過咸水係咪多數都會發霉？ 同埋有冇巴打發生過類似事件可以分享下同保險申訴既過程有冇d 特別野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n附上水舞間圖片幾張<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/184741_02e641ac82c51bed67f24bef77c82a0e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F184741_02e641ac82c51bed67f24bef77c82a0e.png&h=d544174e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/184753_fe27774fbb09af488f4bae01cc71ceb4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F184753_fe27774fbb09af488f4bae01cc71ceb4.png&h=8acae30d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/184758_7b71df39c31e8ecb7ece12acaec7ffce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F184758_7b71df39c31e8ecb7ece12acaec7ffce.png&h=e8898e1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/184806_4efdc4a7e4400075a2d119030df23347.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F184806_4efdc4a7e4400075a2d119030df23347.png&h=ac2654f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8165ecff3e0e00b7461c1533c3c99519a1e8ffb","tid":763714,"uid":22696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:53:06.000Z","msg":"屋企試過之後發現家居保險有分水浸定火燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e20b6adc9b6143ba623d62b6983d7a7b393036","tid":763714,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:53:11.000Z","msg":"海底奇兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb66c49a23ed2cb8ea9859d04ebbb646d5ac71b6","tid":763714,"uid":9450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:53:22.000Z","msg":"關水掣先？"},{"pid":"e151cc46648d2894184c7d99f31b1d933e7708c0","tid":763714,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:55:24.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf26ad27deea1aedf492fc5ca0d6683eb554cf07","tid":763714,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:59:22.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"9b14d217d703e42993360294abfc5d41825aebfb","tid":763714,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb66c49a23ed2cb8ea9859d04ebbb646d5ac71b6","tid":763714,"uid":9450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:53:22.000Z","msg":"關水掣先？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:02:26.000Z","msg":"關左架， 宜家d 水都抽走晒，係擔心d 地板同家俬"},{"pid":"c34d5aaa0aa5d5a51dd6c5cc151e388fbe709da6","tid":763714,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34e20b6adc9b6143ba623d62b6983d7a7b393036","tid":763714,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:53:11.000Z","msg":"海底奇兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class